description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an experienced therapist to join an established team at the Royal Marsden NHS Foundation Trust. The role will be based at our Chelsea site, fixed term until March 2022 and full time, 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be trained to graduate level with experience in groupwork and working in a health care setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like an informal discussion with a member of the team please contact Angela Gillard, Lead Staff Psychotherapy and Counselling, 0208 661 3074.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Angela Gillard, Lead Staff Psychotheraphy and Counselling, angela.gillard@rmh.nhs.uk, 0208 661 3074&lt;/p&gt;
